   27.5.2.4.3:
   Footnote 217 is nonsense unless showmany is corrected to showmanyc.
-> Accepted.
-> See footnote 231.
 
   27.5.2.4.3:
   basic_streambuf::underflow has two Returns clauses. Should combine
